short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Play Freehead Skate new generation, Offline version on your Google Chrome! Popup and without internet!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_GB,es,e:
Freehead Skate, the thrilling skateboarding game, is now available as a Chrome Extension. Embark on an adrenaline-fueled skateboarding adventure right from your Chrome browser. Perform tricks, flips, and stunts as you navigate through challenging skate parks.

With the Freehead Skate Chrome Extension, you can experience the exhilarating gameplay and smooth controls directly in your browser. Master various skateboard tricks, unlock new skate parks, and compete for high scores.

Whether you're a skateboarding enthusiast or love action-packed games, the Chrome Extension version of Freehead Skate offers a convenient and accessible way to enjoy this immersive game. Get ready to showcase your skills and shred the virtual skate parks in this captivating game available at your fingertips.
